data.description: Lovingly maintained, one owner home. 3 bedrooms 1.75 baths, two living areas, large open kitchen. Appliances stay. Ceramic tile in kit and baths. Newer roof plus double pane windows. This home has been well taken care of and it shows. Large back yard with well built storage shed and private covered patio. Fenced front yard with welcoming front porch. 1 car attached garage plus car port. Separate utility/service room. This home is move in ready. Call us today to see it for yourself. A real 10!
